<div id="TabContent" class="tab-content container">
	<div id="ProductDescription" class="container tab-pane fade show active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-description" tabindex="0">
		<p class="p-3">
			純白
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>■ 中心孔距:305mm</li>
			<li>■ 用水量:小號2.9公升，大號3.8公升</li>
			<li>■ 洗淨方式:噴射虹吸式</li>
			<li>■ 潔淨:馬桶排污管上釉</li>
			<li>■ 最低水壓:0.8kgf/㎝²(流動壓)</li>
			<li>■ 最高水壓:7kgf/㎝²(靜止壓)</li>
			<li>■ 搬運警告:若需搬動智慧馬桶，請從下方陶瓷本體處施力搬運；若只抓住上方馬桶座(塑膠部分)，會因塑膠無法承重而造成產品損壞！</li>
		</ul>

		<img class="py-2" src="~/images/propic_01.jpg" alt="" />

		<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JGEj2nhPvDs" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>

		<img class="py-2" src="~/images/propic_02.jpg" alt="" />
	</div>

